                            "V1": "Some older HTML elements, such as <0>&lt;blink&gt;</0>, <0>&lt;font&gt;</0>, and <0>&lt;marquee&gt;</0> are outdated. These elements are no longer supported in modern browsers and can create accessibility issues. Instead of using these elements, you should replace them with semantic HTML elements."
