                            "V1": "In your HTML code, locate the HTML element of <0>&lt;blink></0>, <0>&lt;font&gt;</0>, or <0>&lt;marquee&gt;</0>."
                        },
                        "STEP_2": {
                            "V1": "Replace it with a semantic element:",
                            "1": {
                                "V1": "<0>&lt;blink&gt;</0>: Replace it with a semantic element (e.g.,<0>&lt;span&gt;</0>, <0>&lt;h1&gt;</0>, <0>&lt;h2&gt;</0>). Apply a CSS animation if a blinking effect is required."
                            },
                            "2": {
                                "V1": "<0>&lt;font&gt;</0>: Replace it with a semantic element (e.g.,<0>&lt;p&gt;</0>, <0>&lt;span&gt;</0>, <0>&lt;h1&gt;</0>). Then apply CSS styles for color, font, and size."
                            },
                            "3": {
                                "V1": "<0>&lt;marquee&gt;</0>: Replace it with a semantic container (e.g., <0>&lt;div&gt;</0>). Then apply a CSS scrolling animation."
                            }
                        },
